{"type":"message","id":"9d8f5518","parentId":"7df21b3c","timestamp":"2026-04-28T07:04:30.479Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:449f0d3e-002d-4362-b785-e56c0682c27b Emmy Email Check (Gmail + iCloud)] Check emails in BOTH Gmail AND iCloud and send TWO SEPARATE messages back-to-back.\n\n=== MESSAGE 1: GMAIL ===\nSTEP 1 - Run: gog gmail search 'in:inbox newer_than:1h' --max 50 --account rtg.bobby@gmail.com\n\nSTEP 2 - Classify emails as:\n- URGENT (bills, payments, security alerts)\n- IMPORTANT (jobs, appointments, personal)\n- LOW PRIORITY (promotions, newsletters)\n\nSTEP 3 - Send FIRST message to 8212808444 with format:\n📬 GMAIL — New Mail (X new)\n\n🔴 URGENT:\n• [Sender] — [Subject]\n  └ [1-line summary]\n\n🟡 IMPORTANT:\n• [Sender] — [Subject]\n  └ [1-line summary]\n\n⚪ LOW PRIORITY:\n• [Sender] — [Subject]\n  └ [1-line summary]\n\nIf NO new Gmail emails: '📬 GMAIL — No new emails'\n\n=== MESSAGE 2: ICLOUD ===\nSTEP 4 - Run: himalaya envelope list --account icloud 2>&1 | grep -v WARN\n\nSTEP 5 - For any new iCloud emails, read them: himalaya message read <id> --account icloud\n\nSTEP 6 - Send SECOND message to 8212808444 with format:\n📬 ICLOUD — New Mail (Y new)\n\n🔴 URGENT:\n• [Sender] — [Subject]\n  └ [1-line summary]\n\n🟡 IMPORTANT:\n• [Sender] — [Subject]\n  └ [1-line summary]\n\n⚪ LOW PRIORITY:\n• [Sender] — [Subject]\n  └ [1-line summary]\n\nIf NO new iCloud emails: '📬 ICLOUD — No new emails'\n\nRULES:\n- Send the Gmail message FIRST, then the iCloud message immediately after\n- Only include sections that have emails (skip empty categories)\n- Keep summaries to 1 line\n- Mark action needed with ⚠️\nCurrent time: Tuesday, April 28th, 2026 - 3:04 AM (America/New_York) / 2026-04-28 07:04 UTC\n\nUse the message tool if you need to notify the user directly for the current chat. If you do not send directly, your final plain-text reply will be delivered automatically."}],"timestamp":1777359870467}}
