{"type":"message","id":"ffb9f66a","parentId":"c4343f94","timestamp":"2026-04-28T07:05:11.341Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Gmail has no new emails. iCloud has 4 emails but they're all older (April 27 and older) - not new within the last hour. Let me check the timestamps more carefully:\n\n- ID 9: 2026-04-27 19:06 - this is yesterday, not within 1h\n- ID 8: 2026-04-27 12:20 - not within 1h\n- ID 7: 2026-04-13 - older\n- ID 6: 2026-01-22 - older\n\nSo no new emails in either. I'll send both \"no new emails\" messages.\n","thinkingSignature":"32565796402458f41e30a4c6c9f7b6f0b3e710e5dfe3f7cf18cea8933ea9b016"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rsjnoq78i2hh_1","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","message":"📬 GMAIL — No new emails","target":"8212808444"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":340,"output":193,"cacheRead":19584,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20117,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777359904979,"responseId":"063f8f2125fe3068ec130cf3dfa972b4"}}
