{"type":"message","id":"20fab045","parentId":"57bcabef","timestamp":"2026-04-28T07:05:17.348Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me check the iCloud emails. The envelope list shows some read emails (marked with R flag). Let me check if any are unread. The flags column shows:\n- ID 9: no flags (unread probably)\n- ID 8: ! R (marked important and read)\n- ID 7: R (read)\n- ID 6: R (read)\n\nSo ID 9 is unread. Let me read it.\n","thinkingSignature":"f4c50c52652df6db9f197f700122b58c47207b74c9b79416867adc92e5046e5a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_e05y1y23fytn_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"himalaya message read 9 --account icloud 2>&1","timeout":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":115,"output":139,"cacheRead":19904,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20158,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777359911990,"responseId":"063f8f281239c989f9532822fa1d8bba"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d7ce69d0","parentId":"20fab045","timestamp":"2026-04-28T07:05:18.456Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_e05y1y23fytn_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[2m2026-04-28T07:05:18.001125Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-28T07:05:18.001737Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-28T07:05:18.001761Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-28T07:05:18.001805Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\nFrom: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nTo: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nHello,\n\nOk sounds good. I may have one for that time frame. Just keep in mind they are first come first serve. Once approved, your application stays with us until we can link you to a unit. Once Logan is done, we can begin the process. Any questions feel free to reach out.\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com\n\n\n\n[A picture containing text, font, screenshot, graphics  Description automatically generated]\n\n\n\n________________________________\nFrom: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSent: Monday, April 27, 2026 12:17 PM\nTo: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nGood afternoon, We were hoping sometime before June 4th. I will follow up once Logan completes his portion of the application. Thank you, Robert Galletta                                              \nReport This Email<removed-link>\n\nGood afternoon,\n\nWe were hoping sometime before June 4th.\nI will follow up once Logan completes his portion of the application.\n\nThank you,\nRobert Galletta\n\n\nOn Apr 27, 2026, at 8:20 AM, RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>> wrote:\n\n\nGood Morning,\n\nOnce Logan completes his, I can run the apps. When are you looking to move by so I can make sure I will have one Available?\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com<https://shared.outlook.inky.com/link?domain=royalcoveapts.com&t=h.eJxNjkEOwiAURK_SsLalQAXbVa8Cnx9sRD-h1NgY764sNG7nzeTNk205sqlh51LSxHmm3UagO9pU1g7oyg4Nu9RCxMdyC4VubcqUMJe9DZm2xDNEtOuHzb9KCnXKHYAAiSNqZ3EEpb0dBiHtUSqPPUoujDGq19qMXX8SRktVdVh1uYTOkXP7vECkzX-_-Ar_otcb3UI-gg.MEUCIQCrAoq9O9zx8X-WiCWAUINSyTP-_NOMlxkZwbLwiSoYkQIgeBorTOa8cgxlkQb1ARuodw22Fxfr2BJ6_Md9GJYWmkA>\n\n\n\n<Outlook-A picture .png>\n\n\n\n________________________________\nFrom: rtg.bobby@icloud.com<mailto:rtg.bobby@icloud.com> <rtg.bobby@icloud.com<mailto:rtg.bobby@icloud.com>>\nSent: Saturday, April 25, 2026 1:49 PM\nTo: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\n\nHi Amy,\n\n\n\nI wanted to reach out to let you know that I have completed and submitted my portion of the rental application for Royal Cove. I am currently waiting on my partner, Logan, to finish his part of the application on his end.\n\n\n\nWe are still very interested in a 1 bedroom / 1 bathroom unit. Please let me know if you need anything else from me in the meantime, or if there are any updates on availability.\n\n\n\nThank you,\n\nRobert Galletta\n<#part type=image/png filename=\"/Users/bobbygalletta/Downloads/Outlook-A picture .png\"><#/part>"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1093,"aggregated":"[2m2026-04-28T07:05:18.001125Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-28T07:05:18.001737Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-28T07:05:18.001761Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\n[2m2026-04-28T07:05:18.001805Z[0m [33m WARN[0m [2mimap_codec::response[0m[2m:[0m Rectified missing `text` to \"...\"\nFrom: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nTo: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nHello,\n\nOk sounds good. I may have one for that time frame. Just keep in mind they are first come first serve. Once approved, your application stays with us until we can link you to a unit. Once Logan is done, we can begin the process. Any questions feel free to reach out.\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com\n\n\n\n[A picture containing text, font, screenshot, graphics  Description automatically generated]\n\n\n\n________________________________\nFrom: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSent: Monday, April 27, 2026 12:17 PM\nTo: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nGood afternoon, We were hoping sometime before June 4th. I will follow up once Logan completes his portion of the application. Thank you, Robert Galletta                                              \nReport This Email<removed-link>\n\nGood afternoon,\n\nWe were hoping sometime before June 4th.\nI will follow up once Logan completes his portion of the application.\n\nThank you,\nRobert Galletta\n\n\nOn Apr 27, 2026, at 8:20 AM, RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>> wrote:\n\n\nGood Morning,\n\nOnce Logan completes his, I can run the apps. When are you looking to move by so I can make sure I will have one Available?\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com<https://shared.outlook.inky.com/link?domain=royalcoveapts.com&t=h.eJxNjkEOwiAURK_SsLalQAXbVa8Cnx9sRD-h1NgY764sNG7nzeTNk205sqlh51LSxHmm3UagO9pU1g7oyg4Nu9RCxMdyC4VubcqUMJe9DZm2xDNEtOuHzb9KCnXKHYAAiSNqZ3EEpb0dBiHtUSqPPUoujDGq19qMXX8SRktVdVh1uYTOkXP7vECkzX-_-Ar_otcb3UI-gg.MEUCIQCrAoq9O9zx8X-WiCWAUINSyTP-_NOMlxkZwbLwiSoYkQIgeBorTOa8cgxlkQb1ARuodw22Fxfr2BJ6_Md9GJYWmkA>\n\n\n\n<Outlook-A picture .png>\n\n\n\n________________________________\nFrom: rtg.bobby@icloud.com<mailto:rtg.bobby@icloud.com> <rtg.bobby@icloud.com<mailto:rtg.bobby@icloud.com>>\nSent: Saturday, April 25, 2026 1:49 PM\nTo: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\n\nHi Amy,\n\n\n\nI wanted to reach out to let you know that I have completed and submitted my portion of the rental application for Royal Cove. I am currently waiting on my partner, Logan, to finish his part of the application on his end.\n\n\n\nWe are still very interested in a 1 bedroom / 1 bathroom unit. Please let me know if you need anything else from me in the meantime, or if there are any updates on availability.\n\n\n\nThank you,\n\nRobert Galletta\n<#part type=image/png filename=\"/Users/bobbygalletta/Downloads/Outlook-A picture .png\"><#/part>","cwd":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777359918456}}
{"type":"message","id":"9efc37f3","parentId":"d7ce69d0","timestamp":"2026-04-28T07:05:38.241Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"RC Leasing replied about the apartment. This is an ongoing conversation about finding a new apartment. It's marked as \"!\" flag which might mean important. Let me also check the other unread ones, but from the timestamps they seem older (from April 27, 2026 and earlier). Message 9 is the most recent. The others (7, 8) are from April 27 and April 13 - those seem to have been read already (no new flags).\n\nActually looking at the list:\n- 9: no flags - this is the newest and unread\n- 8: flags \"! R\" - important and read\n- 7: flag \"R\" - read\n- 6: flag \"R\" - read (from January)\n\nMessage 9 is from April 27, 2026 at 19:06 - that's yesterday. It's the only one with no flags so it's unread. The others are already read.\n\nSince the cron is checking \"newer_than:1h\" (last hour) but the iCloud inbox shows all emails (not filtered by time), let me consider what counts as \"new.\" The email from RC Leasing is from yesterday (April 27) - that's not within the last hour. But for iCloud, I'm checking all envelopes without a time filter.\n\nActually, the instruction says to check iCloud emails too. The RC Leasing email from April 27 at 7:06 PM UTC (which is 3:06 PM EDT) - that's 12 hours ago from the current time of 3:04 AM. So it's not exactly \"new\" within the last hour but it's unread and relatively recent.\n\nI should include it as a recent unread email. Let me send the iCloud report with this email.\n\nActually the CRON format says \"newer_than:1h\" for Gmail only, and for iCloud it says to just list and read any new ones. The iCloud inbox doesn't have a time filter - I'm showing all recent emails. The RC Leasing email (ID 9) is the most recent and unread - received April 27 at 19:06 UTC which is about 12 hours ago. That's recent enough to report.\n\n\nNow I'll format the iCloud message with this email.\n","thinkingSignature":"3491caab03da625acd55a2b8e25758d5acb54c98a3a20f6c43df5c4e016446a8"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_sofmq893qzsx_1","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","message":"📬 ICLOUD — New Mail (1 new)\n\n🟡 IMPORTANT:\n• RC Leasing — Re: Looking for new apartment\n  └ Amy from Royal Cove says they may have a unit for the June 4th timeframe, first come first serve — waiting on Logan to complete his application portion","target":"8212808444"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1206,"output":571,"cacheRead":19968,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21745,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777359918459,"responseId":"063f8f2e3f574311cc8cf56aac853e29"}}
