{"type":"message","id":"fce719a0","parentId":"cd3a8306","timestamp":"2026-04-28T07:05:48.383Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I've completed both email checks and sent both messages to Bobby. Here's the summary:\n\n1. Gmail: No new emails\n2. iCloud: 1 new email from RC Leasing about the apartment - it's marked as IMPORTANT since it relates to their housing search and needs Logan to complete his part of the application.\n","thinkingSignature":"f8aed7b73df4cf5676910ef82a34058fdbadc6457cede6f548d6d031e4057479"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nBoth emails checked and reported. Gmail was clear; iCloud had one important message from RC Leasing about the apartment search — they're waiting on Logan to finish his application portion."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":201,"output":101,"cacheRead":21120,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21422,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777359938648,"responseId":"063f8f4240129ba79489d4fe825ac2b7"}}
